<section>

Take a deep breath, it is the last task =]

<br><br>

After validating the message exchange using the message interceptor. Now the choreography is tested without the interceptors and the choreography will be tested from the end user point of view. 

<br><br>

Deploy the <b>car_parking_ws</b> (service developed in the Task 01) (if not running). This can be done by running the
class <em>car_parking_ws/src/test/java/eu/choreos/common/ServiceDeployer.java</em>

<br><br>
<b>Pre-requirements - Setting up the dependencies </b>
<ol>
	  <li> Start the interactiveGuide process by going to interactive_guide directory and running the command: <pre>./study_task.sh 04</pre></li>
	  <li> Start the flightFinder process by going to flight_finder directory and running the command: <pre>./study_task.sh 04</pre></li>
	<li> Start the carParkReservation process by going to car_park_reservation directory and running the command: <pre>./study_task.sh 04</pre></li>
</ol>

<br>
<b>
<ol>
<li>
Read and think about <span style='color:blue'>shouldReturnAConfirmationMessage()</span> acceptance test case in interactive_guide/src/test/java/eu/choreos/ArrivalAtAirportTest.java
</li>
<li>
Run the test case 
</li>
